  m_text: "A curated library of motion presets across five channels \u2014 Move /
    Rotate / Scale / Fade / Color. Assign one per widget state via the spec's \"animations\"
    block, pick per-state presets in any animator's inspector dropdown, or set project-wide
    defaults in Tools \u2192 Neo UI \u2192 Setup (every button hovers, every view
    fades in). This screen itself pops in via the ScalePopIn show preset. Enter Play
    mode to feel hover and press."
